It's anniversary month and PlanetSide 2 turns 12 years old!

To kick off the month we had the Extra Life Game Day!

This years anniversary bundles* are themed around the lore of Auraxis and it's inhabitants, featuring a wide array of cosmetics for your characters in the form of:
  • Banners
  • Banner Frames
  • Decals
  • Knives
  • Titles
  • Infantry Armor and Helmet


Throughout the month we hope you look forward to Thanksgiving, Black Friday and Cyber Monday sales!

Oh and we merged Cobalt and Miller servers. You're welcome!
*12th Anniversary Bundles will be launched on 20th November 2024.
